version_description: The current 5-star chord sheet isn't entirely correct. A few chords are wrong, it's not capo'd according to the piano sheet music, and some of the chords weren't in the exact place.
Chords in the right place, and chord changes only when they actually change.
This tab incorporates elements of the bass line into the chord sequence to make it playable for one guitar. It's in the original key, so you can play along to the song.
